citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"*【新盤票王】柏傲莊I示範單位日日排長龍 終截收2.27萬登記 97後收票新高*<br />\n<br />\n新世界及港鐵合作旗下位置在沙田車公廟路18號的大圍站上蓋新盤柏傲莊I（柏傲莊第1期）周六日開售391伙，價錢629萬起，地址荃灣愉景新城商場3樓的柏傲莊I示範單位由上周六起連日出現排隊人龍，最終截收逾2.27萬認購登記，榮登97後新盤票王，打低2017年荃灣西站全‧城滙2.25萬紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n柏傲莊I自上周五公布價單，周六開始對外開放示範單位後，除了周二因颱風關係而停開外，日日早上均見長長人龍排隊睇示範單位及進行認證登記，周六日人龍更須等候8小時，周日更須要提早截龍，熱鬧場面為近年新盤罕見。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">97後票王。移民撚移左返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa65ff3db83b1b5d9589dbf6f499dbddcf3ecac1","tid":2244293,"uid":221515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"移走唔夠移入多..."},{"pid":"0cef63addd75ccba3f344d904e46d2de3f2bd34b","tid":2244293,"uid":226489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"移到民就唔俾買樓？？"},{"pid":"c83d740861386dea994af6ef51af70799c3c3fae","tid":2244293,"uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ffad5c8562f6bd385a7e2d1543f6b6fccc97c49","tid":2244293,"uid":137694,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c83d740861386dea994af6ef51af70799c3c3fae","tid":2244293,"uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"其實可以點？照你咁講大陸冇人買樓啦"},{"pid":"c472acae3deefdee69c528996d7baadbc796ab81","tid":2244293,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb400a44cecd52a5536e95b6b192a27a5fb874a7","tid":2244293,"uid":5289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"我入左A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45